OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FRecently graduated paramedics say
OL,7,Fthey've been "left in limbo" after the
OL,8,FWelsh Ambulance Service said it is
OL,9,F"not in a position to employ newly
OL,10,Fqualified paramedics this year".
OL,12,FSeveral graduates have told ITV News
OL,13,Fthey feel "extremely disappointed"
OL,14,Fafter "sacrificing so much time"
OL,15,Fundergoing specialist paramedic
OL,16,Ftraining, only to discover there are
OL,17,Fno available jobs.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
