CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FThe service said it was facing a
OL,7,F"difficult financial and operational
OL,8,Flandscape" and that the decision was
OL,9,Fbased "on a range of factors" from
OL,10,Fstaffing levels to workforce
OL,11,Faffordability.
OL,13,FIt has advised graduates to apply for
OL,14,Fother roles, including Emergency
OL,15,FMedical Technicians, which pay less
OL,16,Fand do not require the same level of
OL,17,Feducation as a paramedic.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@JO]
