OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FStudents in Wales can train to become
OL,7,Fparamedics by getting a paramedic
OL,8,Fscience degree at either Swansea
OL,9,FUniversity or Wrexham University.
OL,11,FPeople can also train through a
OL,12,Fvocational route by working as an
OL,13,Fambulance care assistant or trainee
OL,14,Femergency medical technician and
OL,15,Fstudying part-time.
OL,17,FThe Welsh Government said it was
OL,18,Fworking to "address these challenges
OL,19,Fand support graduates".
OL,26,@zD@LOU{D@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/16
