PN,46104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FOne student told ITV News that they
OL,7,Fhave all been left "devastated".
OL,9,FThey said, "We have trained for three
OL,10,Fyears to serve the people of Wales,
OL,11,Fdedicating time and effort to aid the
OL,12,Fjourney. However, the lack of planning
OL,13,Ffrom the Welsh Ambulance Service has
OL,14,Fdevastated every student studying for
OL,15,Fthis degree."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
