FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FAnother said, "I am outraged. I've
OL,7,Fspent the past three years on
OL,8,Fplacement alongside paramedics on the
OL,9,Ffront line, and I've seen firsthand
OL,10,Fhow long people are waiting for the
OL,11,Furgent care they need."
OL,13,F"(We've been) left in limbo with
OL,14,Funcertain futures after committing,
OL,15,Fsacrificing & training so hard to be
OL,16,Ftold we aren't required."
OL,26,@uD@BpmuD@Mpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/16
