OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FCarl Kneeshaw, director of people at
OL,7,Fthe Welsh Ambulance Service, said, "We
OL,8,Fknow this will be deeply disappointing
OL,9,Ffor those hoping to start their
OL,10,Fcareers with us, especially after the
OL,11,Ftime, effort and commitment they have
OL,12,Finvested in their training, but we are
OL,13,Fcommitted to supporting them as they
OL,14,Fconsider their next steps."
OL,26,@oD@dOUvD@[O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/16
