CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FHe added, "For graduates who want to
OL,7,Fbuild a career with the Welsh
OL,8,FAmbulance Service, we would encourage
OL,9,Fthem to explore other opportunities
OL,10,Fwith us, including emergency medical
OL,11,Ftechnician roles, which we expect to
OL,12,Frecruit to throughout 2026, and which
OL,13,Foffer valuable frontline experience,
OL,14,Fongoing development and a potential
OL,15,Froute into future paramedic
OL,16,Fopportunities.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/16
