PN,46108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,F"We would also encourage graduates to
OL,7,Fconsider opportunities with other
OL,8,Fambulance services and organisations
OL,9,Facross the health and social care
OL,10,Fsector, where their skills and
OL,11,Fknowledge will be just as valued.
OL,13,F"We are working closely with our
OL,14,Funiversity partners and Health
OL,15,FEducation and Improvement Wales to
OL,16,Funderstand the impact of this decision
OL,17,Fon graduates and future workforce
OL,18,Fplanning."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/16
