CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FA spokesman for the Unison Welsh
OL,7,FAmbulance branch said, "We are aware
OL,8,Fof the situation regarding paramedic
OL,9,Funiversity students being informed
OL,10,Fthat (there) will be no newly
OL,11,Fqualified paramedic jobs offered by
OL,12,Fthe Welsh Ambulance Service for the
OL,13,Fcoming year.
OL,15,F"Student paramedics at Swansea
OL,16,FUniversity have undertaken publicly
OL,17,Ffunded courses, supported by Health
OL,18,FEducation and Improvement Wales
OL,19,F(HEIW), based on workforce planning
OL,20,Fand the number of clinicians required.
OL,26,@oD@XOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/16
