OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,F"This situation is being driven
OL,7,Fprimarily by wider financial pressures
OL,8,Fplaced upon the ambulance service,
OL,9,Fstemming from funding constraints at a
OL,10,Fgovernmental level.
OL,12,FA Welsh Labour Government spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid, "We are committed to ensuring
OL,14,Four investment in NHS education and
OL,15,Ftraining is supported by meaningful
OL,16,Femployment opportunities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
