OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,F"We are working closely with the Welsh
OL,7,FAmbulance Services Trust (WAST),
OL,8,FHealth Education and Improvement Wales
OL,9,F(HEIW) and universities to address
OL,10,Fthese challenges and support
OL,11,Fgraduates."
OL,13,F"However, the consequences of these
OL,14,Fdecisions are deeply concerning.
OL,16,F"Paramedics trained in Wales, using
OL,17,Fpublic funds, should be offered
OL,18,Femployment as paramedics in Wales."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]uD@AOUxD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/16
