CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FWelsh Conservative Leader Darren
OL,7,FMillar said, "Labour's NHS failures
OL,8,Flaid bare as paramedic graduates told
OL,9,Fto seek work abroad"
OL,11,FMr Millar said the situation was
OL,12,F"staggering and deeply frustrating".
OL,13,FHe added, "We are training paramedics
OL,14,Fat public expense, only to tell them
OL,15,Fthere are no jobs for them in Wales
OL,16,Fand they should consider going abroad.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,F"At a time when ambulance response
OL,7,Ftimes are still far too long, and
OL,8,Fpatients are coming to harm and
OL,9,Fwaiting in pain, this simply makes no
OL,10,Fsense. It is yet another example of
OL,11,FLabour's failure to properly plan and
OL,12,Fmanage the NHS workforce here in
OL,13,FWales."
OL,15,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson told ITV
OL,16,FNews, "Students are being failed, the
OL,17,FNHS is being failed, and patients are
OL,18,Fbeing failed - all by this Labour
OL,19,FWelsh Government and their complete
OL,20,Finability to properly run our health
OL,21,Fservice.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,F"Over decades, Labour have failed to
OL,7,Finvest in the NHS workforce and failed
OL,8,Fto develop an environment that
OL,9,Fsupports talent and allows them to
OL,10,Fstay in Wales to work."
OL,12,FReform UK's James Evans MS said, "This
OL,13,Fdecision makes a mockery of Welsh
OL,14,Ftaxpayers.
OL,16,F"Not only will the Welsh Ambulance
OL,17,FService continue to be understaffed
OL,18,Fand likely continue to miss key life-
OL,19,Fsaving response time targets, but
OL,20,Ftaxpayers are footing the bill."
OL,26,@tD@bOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775146264
OL,3,C'Left in limbo': Paramedics without
OL,4,Cjobs as ambulance service stops hiring
OL,6,FThe Welsh Liberal Democrats' leader
OL,7,FJane Dodds said, "This is a staggering
OL,8,Fwaste of both talent and taxpayers'
OL,9,Fmoney. We are training paramedics at a
OL,10,Fcost of tens of thousands each, only
OL,11,Fto tell them there is no job for them
OL,12,Fat the end of it.
OL,14,F"We should be doing everything
OL,15,Fpossible to keep these highly skilled
OL,16,Fprofessionals in Wales, not pushing
OL,17,Fthem out of our NHS."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/16
